cov-lineages/pangolin-data.name: pangolin-data v1.35
cov-lineages/pangolin-data.body: Release of pangolin-data repository corresponding to [pango-designation version 1.35](https://github.com/cov-lineages/pango-designation/releases/tag/v1.35).  This repository is compatible with pangolin v4.3 onwards.

nextstrain/nextclade_data.name: 2025-09-09--12-13-13Z
nextstrain/nextclade_data.body:
This release contains changes for datasets:

- All datasets
- Mpox virus (All clades) (nextstrain/mpox/all-clades)
- Mpox virus (Clade I) (nextstrain/mpox/clade-i)
- Mpox virus (Clade IIb) (nextstrain/mpox/clade-iib)
- Mpox virus (Lineage B.1) (nextstrain/mpox/lineage-b.1)




## All datasets

Add schema definition url to `pathogen.json`. This is a purely technical change, for convenience of dataset authors. The data itself is not modified.


## Mpox virus (All clades) (nextstrain/mpox/all-clades)

- The 15 newly designated clade IIb outbreak lineages are now included in the dataset. A description of all new lineages is available in this [mpxv-lineages repo document](https://github.com/mpxv-lineages/lineage-designation/blob/master/designation_records/A.2.5-C.1.3-E.3.1-E-4-F.4.1-G.1-etc_2025-09-07.md). A notable new lineage is G.1, the 2025 Sierra Leone outbreak lineage, which is a descendant of A.2.2.
- Sequences released since the last update in April 2025 are now included.
- Add schema definition url to `pathogen.json`. This is a purely technical change, for convenience of dataset authors. The data itself is not modified.




## Mpox virus (Clade I) (nextstrain/mpox/clade-i)

- Sequences released since the last update in April 2025 are now included.
- Add schema definition url to `pathogen.json`. This is a purely technical change, for convenience of dataset authors. The data itself is not modified.




## Mpox virus (Clade IIb) (nextstrain/mpox/clade-iib)

- The 15 newly designated clade IIb outbreak lineages are now included in the dataset. A description of all new lineages is available in this [mpxv-lineages repo document](https://github.com/mpxv-lineages/lineage-designation/blob/master/designation_records/A.2.5-C.1.3-E.3.1-E-4-F.4.1-G.1-etc_2025-09-07.md). A notable new lineage is G.1, the 2025 Sierra Leone outbreak lineage, which is a descendant of A.2.2.
- Sequences released since the last update in April 2025 are now included.
- Add schema definition url to `pathogen.json`. This is a purely technical change, for convenience of dataset authors. The data itself is not modified.




## Mpox virus (Lineage B.1) (nextstrain/mpox/lineage-b.1)

- The 10 newly designated clade IIb B.1 outbreak lineages are now included in the dataset. A description of all new lineages is available in this [mpxv-lineages repo document](https://github.com/mpxv-lineages/lineage-designation/blob/master/designation_records/A.2.5-C.1.3-E.3.1-E-4-F.4.1-G.1-etc_2025-09-07.md).
- Sequences released since the last update in April 2025 are now included.
- Add schema definition url to `pathogen.json`. This is a purely technical change, for convenience of dataset authors. The data itself is not modified.
